- Preferences: guitar-driven classic rock and AOR; energetic, riff-forward records with a live feel; strong musicianship; cohesive album sequencing; organic production and dynamics; full-album (CD) listening experiences rather than shuffled singles; appreciation for extended solos and lively band interplay.
