- Therefore, based on the direct alignment between my explicit preferences (guitar focus, live feel, strong musicianship, cohesive sequencing) and the Classic rock/AOR album’s described features, I choose that CD and reject "The Very Best of Prince" for being a glossy, singles-oriented dance-pop compilation that contradicts my listening values.

